                        <interp inst="t18420704-name-546" type="surname" value="DONOVAN"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18420704-name-546" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN DONOVAN</persName>
                  </hi>. I keep a shoe-shop in Monmouth-street. On the 22nd of June, Gordon came and offered to sell me these hoots—Flatt was with him—I refused to purchase them—I took notice of the boots—those produced are the boots.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18420704-name-547" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18420704-name-547" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
