                        <interp inst="t18420704-name-551" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN ADAMS</persName>
                  </hi>. I live in Whitechapel, and am a pawnbroker. I took in this handkerchief—I cannot swear to either of the prisoners.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Flatt.</hi> I know nothing about it.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Lee's Defence.</hi> I was in bed on the night of the robbery—those who have come up have not spoken a word of truth.</p>
